      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">10% Discount</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Challenge Fee Table -->
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Challenge Entry Fees</h3>

  <p class="mb-4">
    Challenge fees vary by account size. The fees below are for the Legacy model. Fees for Rapid and Bolt should be confirmed on the FundedNext Futures website.
  </p>

  <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mb-6">
    <table class="w-full text-sm">
      <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
        <tr>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Account Size</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Legacy Fee</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Activation Fee</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Monthly Fee</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$25,000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$129</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-teal-600">$0</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-teal-600">$0</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-slate-50">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$50,000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$249</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-teal-600">$0</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-teal-600">$0</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$100,000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$449</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-teal-600">$0</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-teal-600">$0</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <p class="mb-4">
    If you fail a challenge, you can reset at a <strong>10% discount</strong> on the original challenge fee. All payments are final &mdash; no refunds are offered.
  </p>

  <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-4 mb-6">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold text-amber-900 mb-1">No Refunds</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-amber-800">
      All payments are final &mdash; refunds aren't offered. This applies to all challenge models.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Verdict -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-teal-500 bg-teal-50/60 px-5 py-4">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-800 mb-1">Verdict on Futures Pricing</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      The pricing at FundedNext Futures is straightforward. You pay a one-time challenge fee with no activation or monthly charges. Reset fees are discounted at 10% off the original price. Trading commissions and exchange fees should be confirmed on the FundedNext Futures website for current rates.
    </p>
  </div>

