<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <p class="mb-6">
    The specific trading platforms available on FundedNext Futures should be confirmed on their website, as the official futures rules documentation does not detail platform options. The FundedNext Futures website may list available platforms and their features.
